592 (AH_PRIVATE((_ah))->ah_macVersion >= AR_XSREV_VERSION_SOWL || \
593 AH_PRIVATE((_ah))->ah_macRev >= AR_XSREV_REVISION_OWL_20)
594#define AR_SREV_OWL_22_OR_LATER(_ah) \
595 (AH_PRIVATE((_ah))->ah_macVersion >= AR_XSREV_VERSION_SOWL || \

625#define AR_SREV_KITE_11_OR_LATER(_ah) \

627 AH_PRIVATE((_ah))->ah_macRev >= AR_XSREV_REVISION_KITE_11)
628#define AR_SREV_KITE_12(_ah) \

630 AH_PRIVATE((_ah))->ah_macRev == AR_XSREV_REVISION_KITE_12)
